\q1 \v 42 So shall I answer my slanderers,
\q2 For my trust is in Thy word.
\q1 \v 43 Snatch not from my mouth the word of truth,
\q2 For in Thy judgments I hope.
\q1 \v 44 I will keep Thy law continually,
\q2 For ever and evermore.
\q1 \v 45 So shall I walk in wide spaces,
