\q2 The Creator of heaven and earth.
\b
\q1 \v 3 Thy foot He will not let totter:
\q2 He who keepeth thee will not sleep.
\q1 \v 4 Behold, the Keeper of Israel
\q2 Shall neither slumber nor sleep.
\b
\q1 \v 5 The Lord is He that doth keep thee
\q2 Thy shelter upon thy right hand.
\q1 \v 6 The sun by day shall not smite thee,
\q2 Neither the moon by night.
\b
\q1 \v 7 From all evil the Lord shall keep thee,
\q2 The Lord shall keep thy soul.
\q1 \v 8 He shall keep thy going and coming
\q2 From now and for evermore.
\s Psalm CXXII \\ The Joy and the Prayer of the Pilgrims
